This is Perl module LWP::Protocol::ForInstance.

INSTALLATION

LWP::Protocol::ForInstance installation is straightforward. If your CPAN shell is set up,
you should just be able to do

    % cpan LWP::Protocol::ForInstance

Download it, unpack it, then build it as per the usual:

    % perl Makefile.PL
    % make && make test

Then install it:

    % make install

DOCUMENTATION

LWP::Protocol::ForInstance documentation is available as in POD. So you can do:

    % perldoc LWP::Protocol::ForInstance

to read the documentation online with your favorite pager.

